snippet.title: FireDog: Swooce & Rescue // SAGE 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://rippercoyote.itch.io/firedog-swooce-rescue

Blast off in this firefighting adventure! Play as "Caliente" Callie the Pomeranian, newest and lightest member of the Dog City Fire Department. With the help of her high-tech PPE, supercharged firehose, and canine acrobatics, Callie rescues the citizens of Dog City from blazing buildings in the nick of time. Only you can stop the nefarious and elusive Arsoneko and their gang of mischievous Fuegatos before the whole city goes up in flames!

Developed by RipperCoyote
